---
/**
 * Reusable compliance notice shown above every form on the marketing site.
 *
 * Why this matters:
 *  - Viva's email pipeline (Resend) is NOT HIPAA BAA-eligible.
 *  - This site is for marketing leads only (name, email, phone, quiz answers).
 *  - All clinical communication for enrolled patients lives in Charm Health.
 *
 * The notice tells visitors not to send PHI through these forms and points
 * them at the right channel (911) if they are in a medical emergency.
 * Placed above the form fields, not buried at the bottom.
 */
---

<aside class="phi-notice" role="note">
  <span class="phi-notice__label">Heads up</span>
  <div class="phi-notice__body">
    <p>
      <strong>This is not a clinical channel.</strong> Please do not share
      medical details, lab results, or symptoms here. After you enroll, all
      clinical communication moves into our HIPAA-compliant patient portal.
    </p>
    <p class="phi-notice__er">
      <strong>Not for emergencies.</strong> If you are experiencing a
      medical emergency, call <a href="tel:911">911</a> or go to your
      nearest emergency room.
    </p>
  </div>
</aside>

<style>
  .phi-notice {
    background: var(--ink-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--bronze);
    padding: 0.9rem 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.6rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: 0.9rem;
    align-items: start;
    max-width: 560px;
  }
  .phi-notice__label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--bronze);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--bronze);
    border-radius: 2px;
    line-height: 1;
    align-self: center;
  }
  .phi-notice__body p {
    color: rgba(247, 244, 238, 0.85);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    max-width: none;
  }
  .phi-notice__body p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .phi-notice strong { color: var(--paper); }
  .phi-notice__er strong { color: #e76e6e; }
  .phi-notice a {
    color: var(--bronze);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(214, 134, 74, 0.4);
    transition: color 200ms var(--ease);
  }
  .phi-notice a:hover { color: var(--bronze-bright); }
</style>
